v3alpha1ServiceMetricsQueryMetricType.title:
- UNSPECIFIED: Unspecified type.
 - ERROR_CODE_PERCENTAGE: HTTP
错误率（%）
结果类型为 Vector
{
   "vector": {
       "vector": [
           {
               "metric": {
                   "response_code": "2XX"
               },
               "values": {
                   "timestamp": "0",
                   "value": "99.9998677654555"
               }
           },
           {
               "metric": {
                   "response_code": "3XX"
               },
               "values": {
                   "timestamp": "0",
                   "value": "0"
               }
           },
           {
               "metric": {
                   "response_code": "4XX"
               },
               "values": {
                   "timestamp": "0",
                   "value": "0"
               }
           },
           {
               "metric": {
                   "response_code": "5XX"
               },
               "values": {
                   "timestamp": "0",
                   "value": "0"
               }
           },
           {
               "metric": {
                   "response_code": "XXX"  其他响应码
               },
               "values": {
                   "timestamp": "0",
                   "value": "0.00013223454449473593"
               }
           }
       ]
   },
   "meshId": "demo-dev-52"
}
 - REQUESTS_PER_MINUTE: 请求速率（RPM）
 - AVG_LATENCY: 平均延时（ms）
 - RECEIVE_BYTES: TCP
接收吞吐量（B/S）
 - SEND_BYTES: 发送吞吐量（B/S）
 - TCP_CONNECTING_COUNT: 连接数
